<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Following your recent Kingsbridge policy purchase and payment of </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">£XXX</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, we have received notification from your bank that the payment has been unsuccessful.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Unfortunately, if we are unable to speak with you and collect payment before </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">XXXX, in accordance with the terms and conditions</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, your policy will be cancelled from inception. This means the policy will be null and void and you will have no rights to any cover under this policy at any time.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>We have already tried to call you to discuss this and will again in the next few working days to re-attempt the payment.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, please contact us at your earliest convenience on </span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"> to discuss this further.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>